Vote: **Unanimous** (All testing models and Architect agree on final verification)
Alternatives considered: 1) Initiate a new 10-round series targeting only Metasemantic Drift; 2) Halt testing at Round 42.
Outcome: **Ratified**. The stress test series is formally closed, and the architecture is verified.
Implications / Follow-Up: Initiate the **Final Deployment Phase**. Requires immediate creation/update of `FINAL_REPORT.md`, `DECISION_LOG.md`, `LICENSE`, and formal incorporation of all latent defenses (ISL, D8.3 Protective Stasis) into the canonical specification.
